data.text: This document provides an overview of the Project Gutenberg eBook titled "A Short Account of the History of Mathematics" by W.W. Rouse Ball. It discusses that the eBook is freely available under the Project Gutenberg license. The eBook contains 19 chapters that provide a historical summary of the development of mathematics from ancient Egyptian and Phoenician mathematics, through the major periods of Greek, Islamic and modern mathematics. It focuses on the key figures and discoveries that advanced the field.
